@page "/wiki/jinn"
@using PhasmoStatsBlazor.Services

<div class="wiki-container">
	<img src="/Images/GhostIcons/jinn.webp" />
	<div class="wiki-text">
		<h1 class="header-text wiki-header">
			Jinn
		</h1>
		<hr />
		<div class="text-section grid-split">
			<span class="section-header">Hunting Threshold:</span>
			<div class="sanity-container">
				<img src="/Images/SanityIcons/MediumSanity.png" />
				<div class="threshold-text">50%</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<hr />
		<div class="text-section">
			<span class="section-header">Evidences</span>
			<div class="grid-split">
				<div class="sanity-container">
					<img src="@ItemTierService.EmfPath" />
					<div class="evidence-text emf-text">EMF 5</div>
				</div>
				<div class="sanity-container">
					<img src="@ItemTierService.ThermoPath" />
					<div class="evidence-text freezing-text">Freezing</div>
				</div>
				<div class="sanity-container">
					<img src="@ItemTierService.UvPath" />
					<div class="evidence-text uv-text">UV</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<hr />
		<div class="text-section">
			<div class="section-header">Abilities<br /></div>
			<div class="wiki-info">
				The Jinn can drain 25% sanity of one player in the same room or otherwise within 3 meters of it if the fuse box is turned on.
				This will leave EMF level 2 or 5 at the fuse box.
			</div>
			<br />
			<div class="section-header">Inabilities</div>
			<div class="wiki-info">
				The Jinn cannot turn off the fuse box, as doing so would weaken the ghost.
			</div>
			<br />
			<div class="section-header">Hunt</div>
			<div class="wiki-info">
				The Jinn will instantly speed up to a fixed 2.5m/s if the following criteria are met:
				<ul>
					<li>The fuse box is turned on</li>
					<li>The Jinn has line-of-sight with the player it is targeting</li>
					<li>The Jinn is further than 3 meters away from that player</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
